pages.pageText:
My smiling one, I have only now found that you have been imprisoned. I have sent Lord Cynreft askance for lenience in whatever crimes he believes you have committed. Yet, I know in my heart that you could not have brought harm to another. You my happy, carefree soul. You my dearest one. Now that I know you are still alive I will bend my very spirit to bringing you home.

All my love and wishes,

Laylana

stringStats.value: A letter from Laylana to her fiance and love known only as the Jester. It smells of wildflowers.
